{"title": "4 Must-See Cities in Spain", "description": "Here are 4 must-see cities in #Spain! 🇪🇸 

What's your favorite city or place in Spain? 

#travel #spaintravel #traveltips #travelitinerary #travelguide", "top_comments": [{"comment": "I’ve been to all of these cities multiple times. God, I love Spain! Such a beautiful country. Great weather, incredible food, fascinating architecture."}, {"comment": "You must visit Spain anytime but summer ;)"}, {"comment": "I ll go to Malaga as it's the most beautiful province/city for me (the city is a combination of everything big city in spain + the satellite cities and villages are just wonderful)"}, {"comment": "Glad you like our country,I’m from Barcelona🇪🇸🇪🇸"}, {"comment": "Dude, I am from Sevilla: do not come here in the summer. I have no idea why so many people come, you see them struggling in the heat and the sun. Us locals spend most of the day inside until sundown"}, {"comment": "I can confirm Sevilla is a must visit"}, {"comment": "My family and I are planning a vacation to Spain. It’s a very beautiful country and I’m so excited!"}, {"comment": "Beautiful ❤"}, {"comment": "Love Spain great tips 😊"}, {"comment": "Soller, Mallorca is gorgeous.  Love Spain."}, {"comment": "city was so nice"}, {"comment": "Beautiful Barcelona, nice tips bro!"}, {"comment": "I would like to visit every province 👍😊"}, {"comment": "Barcelona is Amazing ❤❤❤"}, {"comment": "🇪🇸❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️"}, {"comment": "Barcelona is also a capital city. Besides, from Barcelona you easily get to Narbonne, Girona, Morella or even Zaragoza or Avignon. For instance."}, {"comment": "Me gusta"}, {"comment": "Gothic Quarter is the worst place to stay in Barce as it is super touristy and not safe at night--there are lots of better options such as Eixample"}, {"comment": "Málagaaa"}, {"comment": "Te amo Barcelona"}]}

{"title": "Half Japanese in Japan", "description": "", "top_comments": [{"comment": "She sounds so sweet, poor girl didn’t deserve any bullying. She’s also beautiful"}, {"comment": "Her voice is so pretty"}, {"comment": "That confidence hit the roof when she spoke japanese"}, {"comment": "They only bullied her because she's beautiful, sweet and unique."}, {"comment": "She didn't deserve the bullying.  She is so very sweet."}, {"comment": "How can anyone bully her? She seems like a sweet kid… people are sick"}, {"comment": "Imagine having to choose between two countries that bully you. It was so sad when she said they bully me less in Japan. They shouldn’t bully her anywhere period. 😢"}, {"comment": "こんな良い人なのにいじめられるとか許せんわ。うちの学校にもアメリカから交換留学生の女の子居たけど皆仲良くて楽しかったけどな。"}, {"comment": "She appears to be authentically kind."}, {"comment": "Her Japanese accent is so soothing and beautiful"}, {"comment": "A normal japanese girl:

The internet: She should be voice actor

Edit: Some people might have misunderstood me, I AM NOT saying that she doesnt have a unique voice. I am just jokingly implying the state above ^^  In fact I think she can be a good Senpai character that teaches her kouhai english (she can talk both japanese and english)"}, {"comment": "めっちゃ可愛い 声優さんになれる"}, {"comment": "she’s so beautiful and wholesome why are people so unkind😭"}, {"comment": "Her speaking Japanese was so sweet and adorable."}, {"comment": "Poor girl. She learned to be humble and kind it seems. She has a good heart."}, {"comment": "「いいよ！」っていう言い方がかわいい🩷"}, {"comment": "She sounds so much more proud and confident speaking Japanese."}, {"comment": "Hearing her beautiful and angelic voice speaking in japanese is so satisfying"}, {"comment": "I could listen to her talk all day. It’s so soothing."}, {"comment": "日本語話した瞬間に可愛さが倍増した！"}]}
